==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Butter-fingered
<hw>But"ter-fin`gered</hw></mhw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Apt to let things fall, or to let
them slip away; not skillful in using the hands; slippery;
careless.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> bumbling, bungling, ham-fisted, ham-handed,
handless, heavy-handed, left-handed.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>butterfingers</ent>⟦br⟧
